{"tid":1732540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［必需］發動持續黎明行動","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:37.000Z","uid":68632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21d908ee39df32d75522153b803759014e895ba5","tid":1732540,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"上星期黎明威力深遠 事實罷在眼前<br />\n只有被罷工 先有足夠人力參與突發運動<br />\n就算交通受阻 但社區運動不受影響<br />\n請堅持 黎明行動"},{"pid":"fa6f8b4221f85d4dda4c0c8595d000c8a0c57a99","tid":1732540,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"c5c99e997a7e47e097ee2b12e6adf0dcca0bda70","tid":1732540,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce12ced008a85a1e5f72b1eccb5c8c9d10088c9","tid":1732540,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>現時尖東商業區街頭企咗好多黑警甴，等班外面班黑警甴散咗先走啦，佢地冇可能永遠企在那裡阻住人返工和開舖，學生們暫時留在理大校內最安全。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>學生可先在 圖書館、課室、飯堂等 溫書和休息，如果黑警甴真係夠膽漠視國際譴責攻入校園，上到法庭都大把抗辯理由，告你地唔入的，總好過現在就貿貿然衝出去被狗拉。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2276718c7505a9a822699d53eb4d095c28262b11","tid":1732540,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy